# Engine 2: Outbound Prospecting — Environment Variables

# Required: Google Gemini API key for AI sequence generation
# Get yours at: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
GOOGLE_API_KEY=your_google_api_key_here

# Optional: App password (default: brainlancer2026)
